      "title": "HNB hosts bi-annual, multi-faith prayer services",
      "author": "Sahan Weerasooriya",
      "body_lines": [
        "Sri Lanka\u2019s leading private sector bank HNB PLC, hosted its bi-annual multi-faith prayer services at HNB Towers, recently.",
        "The ceremony was held to invoke blessings for the country and its people to overcome the ongoing economic crisis with the participation of HNB\u2019s corporate management, senior management and staff. Blessings were also invoked for the staff as they continue on their mission to serve customers during these challenging times.",
        "The multi-faith observance commenced with a Pirith Ceremony followed by a Christian prayer service, an Islamic recital and Hindu invocation. Prayers were also offered for the continued success of the bank, its leadership, management and customers.",
        "SOE reforms vital, although monetary policies to put SL\u2019s economy on right track are on \u2013 CBSL Governor",
